        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".] Jude would hardly have so expressed himself were he himself an apostle, which several expositors certainly do not grant, explaining this mode of expression partly from Jude’s modesty and partly from the circumstance that, except himself and John, the other apostles were already dead.",
